----------------------------
Si Tersoff potential example
----------------------------

Run this example as follows to generate the force constants and show band structure:

# phonolammps in.lammps --dim 2 2 2 -pa 0.0 0.5 0.5 0.5 0.0 0.5 0.5 0.5 0.0 -c POSCAR_unitcell -p

To perform a preliminary optimization of the atoms position in the unit cell (constant volume):

# phonolammps in.lammps --dim 2 2 2 -pa 0.0 0.5 0.5 0.5 0.0 0.5 0.5 0.5 0.0 --optimize -c POSCAR_unitcell -p
